### Biography Aitor Gómez Goiri is a Research Assistant at the [MORElab research group](http://www.morelab.deusto.es/) who has also worked as an Assistant Professor at the [University of Deusto](http://www.deusto.es/). He finished a [double-degree](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Double_degree) on [Computer Engineering and Engineering in Industrial Organization](http://www.deusto.es/servlet/Satellite/Estudio/1110478598746/_ingl/%231102609955027%231120828512741%231120828512859/0/c0/UniversidadDeusto/comun/render?tipoColeccion=Page) in 2008 and a MSc in [Software Development](http://www.diss.deusto.es/) in 2010 at the University of Deusto. Currently he is a PhD student. ### Contact > Aitor Gómez Goiri (aitor.gomez [at] deusto.es)
> MORElab - Envisioning Future Internet
> Deusto Institute of Technology - DeustoTech, University of Deusto
